==Notable residents==

*Zahimara Fantauzzi (born 1993), footballer member of the Puerto Rico women&#x27;s national team
*Heliot Ramos (born 1999), baseball center fielder for the San Francisco Giants
* Rudolph W. Riefkohl (born 1895), Colonel United States Army 1911-1945
* Frederick L. Riefkohl (born 1889), Rear Admiral United States Navy 1912-1947

